Aggr(RangeSum(Above( (　pick(match(v_ViewUptake, 'NFIRST', 'NSECOND', 'NADD', 'NADD2', 'NADD3'),
    num(sum(Dose1st_AGE), '#,##0;-#,##0;-'),
    num(sum(Dose2nd_AGE), '#,##0;-#,##0;-'),
    num(sum(DoseAdd_AGE), '#,##0;-#,##0;-'),
    num(sum(DoseAdd2_AGE), '#,##0;-#,##0;-'),
     num(sum(DoseAdd3_AGE), '#,##0;-#,##0;-')

qStringExpression.qExpr:
=if(GetSelectedCount([Member State])=1, 
pick(match(v_ViewUptake, 'NFIRST', 'NSECOND', 'NADD', 'NADD2'),
'Cumulative number of first doses administered by age group in ',
'Cumulative number of primary courses administered by age group in ',
'Cumulative number of first boosters administered by age group in ',
'Cumulative number of second boosters administered by age group in ',
) & [Member State]
,pick(match(v_ViewUptake, 'NFIRST', 'NSECOND', 'NADD', 'NADD2'),
'Cumulative number of first doses administered by age group in ',
'Cumulative number of primary courses administered by age group in ',
'Cumulative number of first boosters administered by age group in ',
'Cumulative number of second boosters administered by age group in '
) 
& v_EU27_EEA_Title
)
& ' as of '& date(ReloadTime(), 'YYYY-MM-DD')

=if(getselectedcount([Member State])=0, 'Data from '&
pick(match(v_ViewUptake, 'NFIRST', 'NSECOND', 'NADD', 'NADD2'), 
	count(distinct {<[Member State]={"=sum({<[Member State]=>}  Uptake1st_AGE )>0"}>} [Member State]),
    count(distinct {<[Member State]={"=sum({<[Member State]=>}  Uptake2nd_AGE )>0"}>} [Member State]),
    count(distinct {<[Member State]={"=sum({<[Member State]=>}  UptakeAdd_AGE )>0"}>} [Member State]),
    count(distinct {<[Member State]={"=sum({<[Member State]=>}  UptakeAdd2_AGE )>0"}>} [Member State])
)
& ' reporting countries, ')
&'by reporting week '&v_Text_Preliminary
